Class SolrResultDbPojo

  • public class SolrResultDbPojo
extends OpenInfraPojo
    This POJO is a container for a database result of a Solr query. TODO The POJOs must extend OpenInfraPojo to be accessible for the primer class. The UUID and TRID that is provided by the OpenInfraPojo will never be used.

    BTU DBIS
